description: Java class representing branding configuration for a partner in the invoice backend system, including fields for logo URL, primary and secondary colors, notes, and timestamps. It uses JPA annotations for ORM mapping.

classes.name: Branding
classes.description: Entity class that models branding settings associated with a partner, including visual branding elements and timestamps.

methods.name: getId
methods.description: Returns the ID of the branding.

methods.name: setPartner
methods.description: Sets the Partner object associated with this branding.

methods.name: getLogoUrl
methods.description: Returns the URL of the branding logo.

methods.name: setLogoUrl
methods.description: Sets the URL of the branding logo.

methods.name: getPrimaryColor
methods.description: Returns the primary color used in branding.

methods.name: setPrimaryColor
methods.description: Sets the primary color used in branding.

methods.name: getSecondaryColor
methods.description: Returns the secondary color used in branding.

methods.name: setSecondaryColor
methods.description: Sets the secondary color used in branding.

methods.name: getNotes
methods.description: Returns any notes associated with the branding.

methods.name: getCreatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when branding was created.

methods.name: getUpdatedAt
methods.description: Returns the timestamp when branding was last updated.
